data.description: Welcome to Your Updated Pool Home in Sheffield in the highly sought after Westchase area! Nestled within the inviting gates of Sheffield, this meticulously updated gem offers the perfect blend of comfort and style, all while enjoying the added benefit of **NO CDD fees**. With 1,758 square feet of living space, this three-bedroom plus den/study, two-bath home is designed for the modern homeowner seeking both convenience and elegance. The exterior boasts fresh paint, while the interior exudes warmth with a neutral color palette. Enjoy peace of mind with a new roof in 2020 and a new HVAC system installed in 2019. Culinary enthusiasts will delight in the modern stainless steel appliances 2020, including a gas range, granite countertops, refreshed cabinets, and a generous bar area—perfect for entertaining.  Open Concept Floorplan!  The kitchen gracefully overlooks a spacious family room, fostering connectivity and a seamless flow throughout the home.  Indulge in the updated master bath featuring Quartz countertops, dual sinks, a relaxing garden tub, and a frameless shower.  **Home Office** The den/study showcases a custom Murphy Bed and built-in computer workspace—ideal for remote work or as a versatile guest room.  Additional bonus features include hard flooring throughout, both tile and wood floors, and plantation shutters. Step outside to your own private oasis—an inviting screened pool area and a fully fenced yard offer the ultimate setting for outdoor gatherings and relaxation.  This property enjoys a prime location with a vibrant community. Sheffield residents relish proximity to sought-after shopping, delectable restaurants, coffee shops, community playgrounds, top-rated schools, banks, and the library. Additionally, you're just minutes away from downtown Tampa, Tampa International Airport, International Plaza, and easy drives to the stunning Gulf beaches. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a tastefully updated pool home in the heart of Sheffield, Westchase. Schedule a showing today and make this your dream Florida retreat!
